title: Supra Presents Kevin Romar
description:
SUPRA is proud to announce that Kevin Romar is the newest member of the am team. 

"SUPRA's got a sick team," Romar said. "with all the legends and all the ams, and now that I'm on the same team with them, it's unbelievable because I used to watch those guys when I was little."

Director: Dennis Martin
Videography, Edit: Mike Marasco, Dennis Martin
Compositing: Andrew Furlong
